{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she also lost her twin brother in babyhood, so we just know that generation and generation we had twins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no idea why they are saying, step out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we looked at each other, and it's a-- it's a miracle for me till today.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We looked at each other, the three of us, we didn't say one word to each other, and we didn't step out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was really the first link of-- of-- of the chain of our survival.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did not step out as twins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went on, and then, suddenly, I saw a big sign-- Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had no idea what it meant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know, at that moment, that this will be a name that I will remember forever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And under this name was a whole sentence, like an arch, that said, 'Arbeit Macht Frei.' Work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, of course, eventually, we found out that we are in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we progressed in our walk, and then I saw, in front me, a group of German officers, and soldiers, and men and women in striped clothing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this offer, one of the officers, stood out especially.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The first thing what came to my mind when I saw him, I said, oh, my God, is he handsome.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never saw a more handsome man than he is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was 16 and 1/2, and that's what I saw when I saw him first.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was standing there in his uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He had on white gloves, and he had a little stick, and he was pointing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When we came close to him, pointing right and left, life and death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He decided who will live and who will die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this was the famous Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
